data.description: Attention just reduced for a quick closing. Priced below Market value.  Spacious 3 bedroom plus home.  Newer roof and fenced yard with a 2.5 car garage. 2 bedrooms and full bath on the main floor and a 3 bedroom with a walk through to the 4th bedroom or office. Upstairs has a half bathroom. There is a large living room and a formal dining room with a build in china cabinet. Looking for a cash sale or hard money. Sold as is, if inspection it will be for informational purposes only, no repairs or credits or price reduction will be made due to the inspection. This property is a diamond in the rough. Great investment or owner occupant.
